content:
Building on the back of an impressive debut year, with his first two releases surpassing a million streams, and a run of shows supporting Sigrid, Oli Fox has returned with his first new material of 2019 in the form of the radio ready Young.

With pop music missing a real personality in 2019, Oli could well be the charismatic individual to fill that void. Check out Young below.
